{"id": 2734, "genre": 1001, "title": "相比从前，你的听歌习惯发生了哪些变化？", "description": "粉丝刷榜，如今已经没法从流行音乐榜单上找到想听的好歌了。", "record_count": 4270, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201901141707295b7LO09ZsPQTael1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-23T03:00:20Z", "options": [{"id": 324096, "content": "欧美独立音乐控/纯音乐控（后摇，古典）", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585863}, {"id": 324097, "content": "经常想尝试性地看新歌榜单，听着听着就听回了老歌。一看歌手榜单… 这tm都是些谁", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148667}, {"id": 324609, "content": "以前不知道听什么 就什么都听 现在喜欢听古风还有一些老歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996755}, {"id": 324100, "content": "从前是打开网易云直奔排行榜，现在只能抱着自己的小红心涩涩发抖", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565759}, {"id": 327941, "content": "从英文歌洗脑，到薛之谦毛不易。\n我可能经历了什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058013}, {"id": 324101, "content": "原来喜欢随大流现在有自己的风格，喜欢自己的一小圈子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1412144}, {"id": 327173, "content": "在自己的歌单里一听听一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1582069}, {"id": 324102, "content": "听腻了那些爱来爱去的歌，转听金属疯狂甩头去了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1556987}, {"id": 324104, "content": "以前追喜欢的歌手，一听一张专辑。现在从综艺、推介、猜你喜欢逮到一首喜欢的就无限循环一阵子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565776}, {"id": 324105, "content": "酷狗→网易→bandcamp→rateyourmusic", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927309}, {"id": 325897, "content": "轻音乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573723}, {"id": 324106, "content": "听一整张专辑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335095}, {"id": 324107, "content": "以前听周杰伦，现在还是听周杰伦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565796}, {"id": 324108, "content": "以前的歌是自己找，现在就听推荐歌单", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1429979}, {"id": 325132, "content": "现在就有好多，喜欢自己喜欢的歌手不要火起来。好多歌，火了之后，就变了。各种因素", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1569982}, {"id": 324109, "content": "以前只听或者说只接触到流行，现在几乎什么都听（除了大部分纯说唱与重金属）。当然有所偏爱，但我觉得我听歌的范围无疑是扩大了不少。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455573}, {"id": 325133, "content": "截至如一喜欢着爵士", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1542109}, {"id": 324110, "content": "去年网易云年度歌单报告指出，我的风格成谜，我是根据环境地点心情的不同而喜欢不同音乐，甚至因为爱的人喜欢某一种风格而陶醉其中，但相比而言，我的私人歌单里永远都会是经典老歌占据半壁江山，那记载了我的回忆，承载着太多，令人满意舍弃，现如今一些新歌，我听起来，感觉还缺那么一点底蕴和沉淀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565792}, {"id": 324878, "content": "听歌，还是经典的好听，百听不厌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1568952}, {"id": 325135, "content": "小时候喜欢听华语的，现在只听外语的。小时候喜欢听流行的，现在喜欢找老专辑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 516412}, {"id": 324112, "content": "听摇滚乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386990}, {"id": 324113, "content": "流行乐— 古风 —轻音乐  —英文—电音", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1563080}, {"id": 324370, "content": "在听电音的路上一去不复返", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 218589}, {"id": 324115, "content": "抖音毁了很多好听的歌曲\n我自己更倾向于日文歌，轻音乐，这两块还没太被抖音无染", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1564864}, {"id": 324116, "content": "以前听心情，现在听故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1469218}, {"id": 334870, "content": "老歌更有味道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298793}, {"id": 324118, "content": "以前喜欢听伤感情歌，现在喜欢听小众民谣", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1546500}, {"id": 324374, "content": "对各种流派和风格都持更开放的态度", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191455}, {"id": 324119, "content": "几乎只听acg相关了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565814}, {"id": 324376, "content": "从流行到古典", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566608}, {"id": 324121, "content": " 现在开始对建国前老歌情有独钟…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001376}, {"id": 324122, "content": "以前听歌听韵律，现在听歌总想揣摩歌词。从重“曲”到重词☺️☺️☺️", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457838}, {"id": 324378, "content": "喜欢旋律比较舒服的，不太关注歌词的内容和意义。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419276}, {"id": 324123, "content": "现在不喜欢看云村的评论了，因为段子太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565828}, {"id": 324124, "content": "以前听旋律，现在听歌词，总有一句打动你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1565729}, {"id": 324380, "content": "喜欢民谣，赵雷，李志，陈鸿宇，房东的猫，大多数都听过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1444244}, {"id": 324125, "content": "爱听的歌都在steam的原声包里", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1455119}, {"id": 324126, "content": "爵士古典民歌有人吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218042}, {"id": 324127, "content": "越听越往靠前的年代听了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163066}, {"id": 326943, "content": "喜民谣，但费烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1578105}, {"id": 324128, "content": "越来越喜欢古风歌了√", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555935}, {"id": 324384, "content": "中文歌很久没听了，为什么不想听呢？可能是因为好的填词人越来越少了？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 614107}, {"id": 324129, "content": "以前喜欢千禧年国语，现在喜欢90年代粤语哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123171}, {"id": 326433, "content": "一直循环一个歌。\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1576599}, {"id": 324130, "content": "好兄弟punk band 的编曲贝斯，开了个录音棚，了解了修音工程，再也不想听口水歌了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262113}, {"id": 324131, "content": "相比十年前大学时代，现在工作n年只听自己认识的乐队。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960025}, {"id": 324132, "content": "抖音快手流行什么就不听什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1492559}, {"id": 324136, "content": "我从国语到欧美。。。emm", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462655}, {"id": 324392, "content": "以前喜欢听老歌，一个年轻人活的像中年人似的，过后听民谣，流行歌曲，现在十八岁，爱听电音，抖腿节奏控。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1566639}, {"id": 324137, "content": "以前都是从排行榜选歌，现在是用排行榜筛除。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470846}]}